Text:
Hi babe, how was your journey to Kaduna.

I hope it wasn't stressfull

Calvary greetings brother Sam, I trust you are doing fine. It been about 6 months since you were last seen fellowshiping with us, I hope all is well, in this period of economic meltdown there is no better time to draw closer to God. May the good Lord keep us all from temptations. I hope to see you fellowship with the brethren come sunday. The Lord be with you always my brother
Thank you Pastor
Hey, I've got a new scam idea. we need to discuss.
Sure, I'm in. What's the plan this time?
Let's create a fake investment website and lure people into investing in a non-existent cryptocurrency. We'll promise huge returns.
Sounds good. Do you have the website ready?
Yes, use the same Bitcoin wallet address as before: 16AtGJbaxL2kmzx4mW5ocpT2ysTWxmacWn.
I feel you man, I am in on this fully, but not high value client we go Target this time around I.
Sure, enough of this text messages. Meet me over Google Meet byt 10pm. Here is the meeting link: https://meet.google.com/abcd-efgh-ijkl
Alright man, I go join wen time reach
Hey Egbon, I've set up a new website for our next venture. Check it out: https://apyeth.gifts/
Nice work, Sammy. I'll take a look at the site. Are we using the same tactics as before?

Yes, but this time we're targeting investors with promises of exclusive access to a "revolutionary" crypto currency technology. The website layout is designed to mimic legitimacy, complete with fake testimonials and fabricated investment portfolios.
Sounds convincing. Payment gateway nkor? Are we still using the same Bitcoin wallet address?
No, I've set up a new wallet address for this operation. Here it is: 1K1KMHpynJHQRbhzKHyik6yaJuQYxSaZCm
Got it. I'll update the payment instructions on the website accordingly. When we dey go live?

We'll lauch the website next week. In the meantime, spread the "good news" discreetly through our Network of affilliates and social media channels, telegram is very important. We want to create a buzz without attracting unwanted attention.
Understood omo iya mi. I'll handle the promotional activities and monitor for any potential leaks. This one go be bang Inshallah
